{"type": "article", "id": 54879, "title": "气泡饮料打开后就很难保存？这个盖子会帮到你｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-07-03T23:13:12Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 51548, "name": "Ramos & Bassols"}, {"id": 18311, "name": "Native Union"}, {"id": 51509, "name": "Magisso"}, {"id": 3255, "name": "Menu"}, {"id": 51549, "name": "Umiar"}, {"id": 30910, "name": "Taeg Nishimoto"}, {"id": 51550, "name": "Maria Kivijärvi"}, {"id": 51551, "name": "William Battaglia"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 91, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180703215218nz6xl5D3pGwFr2b0.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Smarter Seal by William Battaglia</h3><p>很多人都是苏打水、碳酸饮料爱好者，但易拉罐装饮品的最明显缺点是，一旦打开很难保存。这些气泡饮料如果长时间开启，内部二氧化碳气体就会逃逸到空气当中，这就大大影响了饮料本身的口感。</p><p>设计师 William Battaglia 为此提出了一个名为 Smarter Seal 的解决方案，可以保持饮品的新鲜和安全。它可以直接卡在易拉罐顶部，保证罐体内部的液体不受侵害。售价 3.99 美元起，<a href=\"https://smarter-seal.com/collections/smarter-seal-clear-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703215313ZKE2Gdx3z8OBjca6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703215314iPxo9CMvbF7skept.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703215314nWGkMxBUtsX8ulcN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703215314eEm4WVzI07OGxYcr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703215314BoHiIOl342A0d1mX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Phare Lamp by Umiar for Menu</h3><p>丹麦家居设计品牌 Memu 最近推出了名为 Phare 的便携式 LED 灯具，操刀设计的是波兰工作室 Umiar。它使用方便，重量轻，便于携带，配有可充电电池，几乎可以在任何环境中使用。</p><p>它没有多余的、装饰性的元素。为了在不需要电源插座的情况下使用，Phare 配置的可充电电池起了大作用，续航 10 小时，它可以根据需要自由放置，悬挂或带到户外。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703215346jMwXnP6r3iN7EV1D.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703215346Fn4Jjgb9aVweXf0y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703215347ufL7EkjxhFgPtBNl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666967\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703215347WB5PVUnXOERk6qu1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703215347XEUKjqFQvtPmaeJk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201807032153474Yq3859BWXcp2jRi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://menu.as/en/lightning/phare-led-lamp/#\" rel=\"nofollow\">MENU</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Element No.2.0 Hook Shelf by Maria Kivijärvi for Magisso</h3><p>近些年，收纳已经超越了它最传统的意义，有了更多玩法，不再是干净整洁地藏起来，而是把收纳变成了展示的一部分，甚至可以成为家居装饰元素。</p><p>比如芬兰设计品牌 Magisso 推出的这款 Element No.2 Hook Shelves，它是一个桦木胶合板制作的圆环收纳架，附有白蜡木贴面，用来收纳手套、围巾、钥匙和其他杂物，增加收纳空间的同时，也是一个极简主义风格的空间装饰品。除了圆环状款式，另有半圆形款式，可以挂置在衣架上，也可以贴于墙面使用。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703215430w3yI5irZgY6bds24.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.258929\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703215430FjuRl1qzSOvH7IKD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.793945\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703215430z2V6hYCg1lmbuPtR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.793945\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703215430UIEcunaypstQLZXi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.793750\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703215430wdgq8jI1GhapTx36.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.259843\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703215431TUKnhEe7LldYgktw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.259843\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://magisso.com/products/element-no-2-0-hook-shelf-circle/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Magisso</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Rose Cables by Native Union</h3><p>书房、卧室中总有条因长期使用而破损的传输线，在街上电源线时突然接触不良的恼人经验。成立于 2009 年的配件品牌 Native Union 针对这种情况，推出了专业级坚韧防弹衣材质的电缆线，兼具功能性与美感。</p><p>设计师 Igor Duc 与 John Brunner 以生活周遭为灵感，设计出独特配色与花纹的编织感电缆线，防弹衣料专用的 DuPontTM Kevlar® fiber 最高强度织维材质，三层式防护包覆纯铜双层线芯，抗拉扯、PVC 耐高温腐蚀与极速充电。</p><p>化繁为简的欧式设计风格，在忙乱中还能展露个人性格品味，搭配的意大利手工鞣制皮革扣件，简洁方便随身出游携带。最新加入的玫瑰粉色，是时下流行的色彩趋势，呈现出更柔和、更女性化的特质。售价 200 港币起，<a href=\"https://www.nativeunion.hk/charging/cables/\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703215531iqSrgKGNs6wu0QZd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.731250\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703215532PDtlAKecfoXp4uIL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.675000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703215532taTmD5f0MsL4bZyF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703215533bqWlQxhgUKzD7sHy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.585156\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703215533qbWF5QpOdmsl6aXV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703215533z3t7QTMUfDogWHkN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703215535Fw6CMk8axh2DXzcf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Branca Collection by Ramos &amp; Bassols </h3><p>NIRU Slow Creations 是总部位于巴塞罗那 Ramos&amp;Bassols 设计工作室组建的创意品牌，最近他们推出了第一个系列 Branca。这个系列采用实心橡木手工制成，配备 LED 技术，长长的灯柱会大面积 散发出温暖的光线。</p><p>每盏灯都有一个集成的调光器来调节灯光的强度，可以用作吊灯、落地灯以及台灯。售价 330 欧元起，<a href=\"https://www.nirubarcelona.com/shop\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703215737JTfwsnELDQk1r6lP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703215737WgEGho605O7dXtMn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703215737XgfBLWCV2vKMoGrk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703215737JxkKfEiDezvyU1s9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.578000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703215737wStPQULk1OKGHVY4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703215737ba2hZOTCGeM9XBKI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.862000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703215738vx82mAYuFtSLphoI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Llegado by Taeg Nishimoto</h3><p>Llegado 是一款造型独特的三脚凳，由再生纸浆制作而成。它是设计师 Taeg Nishimoto 对纸浆结构硬度的一次探索，也是以回收纸浆为设计材料的全新尝试。</p><p>凳脚的材料是高密度聚乙烯合成纸，随后用水饱和纸浆混合胶水刷在凳脚模型上。该层纸浆混合物很快在模型上附着并形成 1 厘米厚膜。取一根 33 毫米周长的木杆并放置在平坦表面，将凳脚模型沿木杆长向围合，两侧张开如翼状。最后将这个组合而成的模型放置在弯曲的金属网板上自然风干。</p><p>凳面也是同样的制作方法，但凳面的风干时间会更长。随着纸浆的风干，表面会产生不可预知的纹理，为每一个凳子创造独特的花纹。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703215809EoVCq9cQa1KZesmz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703215809ZUdOKvQu94DonGit.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.933333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703215810YCHDJNM7eWK6PEGv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703215810eQIRM0Fqrx4tkNSW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.732292\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201807032158101rvfeX6tAdNDcP0l.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.771875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703215810y1mrKqlbEvGCsh2T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.933333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180703215811KcLlRyNXtTEj4P2w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://cargocollective.com/taegnishimoto/LIQUID\" rel=\"nofollow\">Taeg Nishimoto</a></figcaption></figure></div>"}